<i>♪ as being loved by you ♪</i>

1338
01:06:50,041 --> 01:06:53,540
<i>♪ Fame is a gun
and I point it blind ♪</i>

1339
01:06:53,541 --> 01:06:56,999
<i>♪ Crash and burn, girl
